Description:
Spacious With pleasant Views
Located in the stylish Conder complex, this immaculate apartment is the perfect home for those seeking luxurious apartment living or a solid investment.
Located on level 10 and offering the discerning buyer the comforts of one very large bedroom with floor to ceiling windows leading to a private balcony, an open plan living/dining, a designer kitchen with Miele appliances, bathroom with Laundry, central heating and cooling throughout, one dedicated car space and a separate storage cage.
Residents have access to a 25m indoor pool, fully equipped gym and a landscaped garden with BBQ facility located on level 2.
For a private inspection call Richard 0437 250 964 or Carmen 0481 794 883.

Description:
A Flinders Wharf Favourite With Yarra River Views
With a picturesque location alongside the iconic Yarra River, and right on the cusp of South Wharf and Yarras Edge precinct while also having easy access to all that the CBD has to offer, this gleaming two bedroom, two bathroom apartment in the sort after Flinders Wharf complex will exceed your expectations.
With a light filled floor plan perfect for relaxed living, this 15th floor residence is fitted with bright floor-to-ceiling windows, excellent stone benches, modern roller blinds and quality carpet. River and Bay views at sunset can be enjoyed from the large undercover balcony, while there is an abundance of space in the central living zone to lounge and dine.
The elegant kitchen has a practical and contemporary edge and is complete with breakfast bar and stainless steel gas appliances. The master bedroom is a peaceful sanctuary that has dual built-in robes and an ensuite, while the 2nd bedroom also enjoys a BIR with ensuite and its own private balcony with north and east views.
Further extras include a quality powder room, separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, video intercom entry and secure car space in addition to a building concierge, indoor pool, gym, spa, sauna and steam room.
This apartment complex has an outstanding riverside spot where you can dine at superb ground floor eateries including the Sea on Quay, Pud Thai Vs Pho, Byblos Bar and Restaurant and The Wharf Hotel. Seafarers Bridge gives you easy access to the South Wharf Promenade and DFO shopping across the Yarra River, while youâ€™re also near Crown Casino, Batman Park, Spencer Street trams and Southern Cross Station.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
SUPERB 2B/R PLUS STUDY CORNER APARTMENT WITH 270 DEGREE VIEWS OF THE CITY, BAY AND MARINA.
From the 21st floor in Mirvacs' flagship "Array" tower you will enjoy an exclusive, secure lifestyle and marvel at some of the best views of the City, Yarra River, Port Phillip Bay and marina that will never be built out.
Offering 121 sqm of luxury living plus 10 sqm of protected balcony this north east facing apartment enjoys the morning sun and with duel zone ducted heating and cooling you can relax in comfort no matter what is going on outside.
Comprising two bedrooms, plus a study or small 3rd bedroom if needed, walk in robe and large en-suite to the master and built in robes in the second.
An excellent kitchen features Meile appliances, ample bench and cupboard space, computer desk and a good sized living area that features floor to ceiling windows to maximize the views. A separate laundry, two toilets, two car parks ( both close to the lift ) and a large storage cage.
Top quality Gainsville furniture can be sold with the property.

Description:
Rare Waterfront Opportunity
Located in the heart of NewQuay, with a promise to deliver sophisticated modern character, stunning quality, and a convenient waterside location, this one bedroom apartment in the SOLD OUT Marina Tower development is a rare opportunity!
This building designed by DKO Architecture has the potential to become an iconic building for NewQuay, Docklands and Melbourne. Available to both local and offshore purchasers, opportunity to take advantage of huge stamp duty savings may be applicable.
Positioned on the 17th level, this superb apartment encompasses a stylishly contemporary interior and floor-to-ceiling windows allowing for great natural light.
Additional features include:
- Quality Miele appliances,
- Open plan living and dining area,
- Views facing the Bolte Bridge and the bay.
Luxurious resort style amenities include:
- Swimming pool on level 7,
- Cinema,
- Library,
- Private meeting rooms,
- Hotel restaurant, cafe and retail on the ground floor.
This freehold development integrates a 7-storey hotel with a total of 269 rooms and two residential towers (43 and 36 levels high), comprising of 471 apartments. The hotel will be managed by the Starwood Hotels and Resorts Worldwide (which own Sheraton, W Hotels, St Regis, to name a few) under the name Four Points By Sheraton Melbourne Docklands Hotel.
Ideal to invest or owner-occupy and situated only moments from public transport and various shopping and dining options, this location is second-to-none.
Estimated completion is early 2018.

SMART DOCKLANDS ONE BEDDER
Whether adding to your portfolio or taking your first step on the property ladder, this smart one bedroom apartment in the low-rise Mariner Complex should be at the top of your list, with low body corp fees and expected returns of over 6%.
Comprised of an open plan kitchen/living area, with a stylish kitchen featuring timber veneer cabinets and stainless steel appliances, the north facing, sun drenched living area opens up onto a balcony with an impressive view of the Melbourne Star. Description:
Chic Docklands Townhouse
Be impressed by this 2 bedroom townhouse, right in the heart of Harbour Town that is 'move-in' ready. Enter through the huge common quadrangle, via a secure lift, into your own spacious courtyard, perfect for barbecues in summer and soaking up the sun.
The open plan living room leads past the kitchen and out to a spacious private balcony with views of the Bolte Bridge. The contemporary kitchen comprises of stainless steel appliances and granite bench-tops, with loads of cupboard space and ideal for cooking up a storm. A powder room with space for storage complete the ground floor. Upstairs, both generously sized bedrooms include huge built-in robes and plenty of natural light. They are serviced by a large, modern bathroom containing a separate bath and double shower. Split system heating & air-conditioning, modern fixtures & fittings, two secure car parks and a storage cage complete this chic Docklands townhouse.
With public transport, a world class shopping precinct, and an array of waterside restaurants on your doorstep, this must see townhouse is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

A sleek and stylish Docklands package that is accompanied by unbelievable views of the Yarra River and the edge of the CBD, this sensational north-facing two bedroom, one-bathroom apartment needs to be high on your property list! A practical and open floorplan caters for all types of buyers, meanwhile floor-to-ceiling windows and quality fittings and fixtures makes everyday living a delight. The sizeable living and meals hub opens out to a balcony that is undercover and features special marina views, while home cooks will fall in love with the ease of the kitchen which owns an island bench and stainless steel appliances. Both Bedrooms include BIR, central bathroom with European laundry, ducted heat/cool, video intercom, secure car space, and access to RekDek incl. gym, pool, spa, steam room, & sauna. Embrace the waterside lifestyle and enjoy great surrounding attractions including South Wharf and DFO shopping, Southbank Promenade, Crown Casino, Etihad Stadium, trams, & Southern Cross Station.
To secure the ultimate in sophisticated Docklands living, be sure to arrange your private inspection today!

Description:
FANTASTIC VIEWS FROM FABULOUS APARTMENT
Delivering spectacular water and city views from the 21st floor of the sought after Nolan Complex is this irresistible apartment in New Quay. Comprising of 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 2 car spaces, this Docklands dwelling possesses space and elegance, as well as floor to ceiling windows that present a stunning vista of Victoria Harbour up to Etihad Stadium.
The generous living area opens up onto a massive, covered balcony with stunning harbour views â€“ perfect for alfresco dining or a refreshing beverage at the end of the day. The stylish kitchen comes complete with dishwasher, stainless steel appliances, concealed fridge, and stone bench-top island breakfast bar. The large master bedroom boasts massive built-in-robes, and a chic, modern en-suite. The second bedroom is also generous in size, and includes plenty of storage with its built in robes. Both bedrooms have balcony access with loads of natural light. The central bathroom completes this fab package with its clean, contemporary finishes, ample storage, and separate bath and shower. Euro-laundry, central heating/cooling, secure swipe and intercom entry, 2 car spaces, and a storage cage round out this immaculate inner-city pad.
Typical of modern apartment living, additional facilities for residents include a fully equipped gym and heated pool. With public transport, world class shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this must see apartment is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

Description:
Corner Elegance at Watergate
Perfectly positioned in a highly desirable corner position is this outstanding two bedroom, two bathroom apartment located in Docklands award-winning Watergate complex. Immaculately presented, this light-filled, stylish and generously proportioned apartment offers brilliant park and pool views, an elegant balcony, a fresh and modern kitchen with marble stone bench tops, quality stainless steel appliances and a breakfast bar. Two spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms, including the main bedrooms beautiful ensuite offering unforgettable luxury.
Features of this large home include:
- Natural light with floor to ceiling windows
- A wonderfully defined living area
- Fully functional kitchen with stainless steel appliances and breakfast bar,
- Two spacious bedrooms with built-in wardrobes,
- The main bedroom with ensuite
- Private balcony
- One secure undercover car park
Recreational facilities within the Watergate building include a full size swimming pool, gym and sauna for residents, with a multi-purpose sports area located just outside the complex.
This is a great opportunity for owner occupiers or astute investors! Location is perfect; with a tram stop being just downstairs, 500 meters from Southern Cross Station, cafes, restaurants and major shopping precincts within a stone's throw.
Call Felicity Bourke now for private viewings 0428 064 846.

Description:
East Facing Waterfront Apartment
Bathed in natural light with captivating City and Water views across to the Casino, this spacious apartment is in the sought after Flinders Wharf building.
Offering the discerning buyer the comforts of 2 generous size bedrooms, master with walk-in robes and en-suite, a deep relaxing bath separate shower and double vanity in the main bathroom, large living/dining adjoining modern kitchen with quality stainless steel appliances, stone bench tops and ample cupboard space. Other features include central heating and cooling, floor to ceiling windows, fabulous balcony providing outlook across the Yarra and Crown Casino, 2 secure under cover car space in the form of a tandem car space and resident access to the fabulous facilities which include a heated indoor lap pool, spa, sauna, steam-room and gymnasium.
The building is within walking distance to South Wharf, DFO, Crown Casino and all the beauty that Melbourne has to offer.
For inspection call Richard 0437 250 964

Description:
GREAT ENTRY PRICE UNIT RIGHT IN THE HEART OF DOCKLANDS!
This stylish one bedroom apartment is located in the much sought after "Montage" low rise apartment complex. Position is perfect with landscaped gardens and a park at your front door.
Offering one generous size bedroom with a BIR and stylish bathroom, hostess style kitchen with stainless steel appliances and stone bench tops, spacious open plan living/dining area opening onto the terrace and a/c-cooling & heating to complete this fantastic package.
The location itself is ideal, with free trams just around the corner, banks, grocery shopping, eateries, cafes, and speciality shops all in close proximity. Etihad Stadium is also within walking distance, along with Harbour Town Shopping centre, and Southern Cross Station.
Currently leased out at $420 per week unfurnished, this is a great return on investment!
